        {
            "_id": "r5WgyRN7xTAUNicy",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneThreeActions.webp",
            "name": "Bloody Reaping",
            "sort": 600000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> to <span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span></p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The redcaps in the brigade wildly swing their halberds and sickles at each enemy in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:10], with a @Check[reflex|dc:26|basic|options:area-effect] save. The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[(1d10+2)[slashing]|options:area-damage,bloody-reaping-one]</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(2d10+9)[slashing]|options:area-damage,bloody-reaping-two]</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(3d10+10)[slashing]|options:area-damage,bloody-reaping-three]</p>"
                },
                "frequency": {
                    "max": 1,
                    "per": "round"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
